outputs.output_descr: The objective of this project is to implement a nation wide incentive program to encourage the retrofit of CFC-12 based mobile airconditioning (MAC) unit and to supply equipment suitable fo assuring correct servicing, retrofittin and recovery and recycling of regrifgerants to the MAC and refrigeration service sub-sectors.

project_descr: Implementation of the Retrofit Mobile air-conditioning Programme- Technical Assistance for the Refrigeration Service and Mobile Air-Conditioning Sectors
